data.description: Step into luxury living with this captivating colonial, a true masterpiece nestled in Walden, NY! Spanning just over 3,400 square feet and boasting Valley Central Schools, this home is a showstopper from the moment you arrive.  Indulge in the grandeur of 9-foot ceilings as you explore the stunning interior, featuring 4 bedrooms plus an office/den and 2.5 bathrooms. Need more space? The finished basement offers endless possibilities for entertainment or relaxation.  Located at the end of a serene cul-de-sac, this home boasts a fenced-in 1/4 acre property, ensuring privacy and tranquility. Enjoy summer days by the above-ground pool or host gatherings on the spacious 21' x 10' back deck, complete with a backyard patio and hardtop gazebo for al fresco dining. Inside, convenience meets elegance with a second-floor laundry and a fully renovated kitchen (2019) that's a chef's dream. Recent upgrades include new A/C (2018) and hot water heater (2018), ensuring comfort and peace of mind. With a 2-car garage, private vinyl fencing, and meticulous attention to detail throughout, this home is a rare find that promises a lifestyle of luxury and leisure. Don't miss your chance to make this Walden wonderland your own!
